      <title>菲律宾继续进行调查，杜特尔特跳过质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾国家调查局将继续调查副总统萨拉·杜特尔特对总统费迪南德·马科斯发出的暗杀威胁，此前她周三第二次未出面接受问询。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/philippines-says-probe-to-go-ahead-as-duterte-skips-questioning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 03:09:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融家尹永康寻求在调查升级之际继续抗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着韩国总统尹锡烈戒严宣言的调查不断深入，且另一起弹劾案即将出现，他似乎准备继续战斗，而不是提前下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/s-korea-s-yoon-prefers-impeachment-over-quitting-chosun-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 01:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将阻止新日铁交易，美国钢铁价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，一旦本月晚些时候交易被交回给拜登，拜登总统计划以国家安全为由正式阻止美国钢铁公司以 141 亿美元的价格出售给新日本制铁公司的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-set-to-finally-kill-nippon-steel-s-proposed-takeover-of-us-steel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 20:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
